{"tid":2275202,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"BLACK PINK熊貓爭議，YG決定不上傳節目，中網民不接受並繼續狙擊","createTime":"2020-11-07T03:45:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-07T07:59:02.000Z","uid":38539,"like":8,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"1d34707db9561a529ccec9ae182416d2bfcb559f","tid":2275202,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T03:45:29.000Z","msg":"早前韓國女團BLACK PINK爆出爭議，她們在YouTube頻道的真人騷《24/365 with BLACKPINK》日前公開預告時，因為化了妝接觸出世100日的熊貓BB，因而遭到大陸網民炮轟。<br />\n<br />\n對於BLACK PINK受到大陸網民的指摘，她們所屬的YG事務所今日就表示原定今日播出最後一集《24/365 with BLACKPINK》的相關內容，決定保留不上傳，同時強調：「愛寶樂園熊貓相關的BLACK PINK的飼養員體驗是在專業獸醫和飼養員的參與下，嚴格遵守防疫管理及衞生守則進行拍攝的。<br />\n<br />\n對於YG方面決定不上傳相關片段，大陸網民依舊不滿，更指YG及BLACK PINK方面未有就事件道歉，又指YG的解釋沒有說服力。<br />\n<br />\n更多詳盡內文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201107/3RSPWCT6QRCKRFXAXTBSIPA3AI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201107%2F3RSPWCT6QRCKRFXAXTBSIPA3AI%2F&d=J7URIij%2BjV7QbFiEH5rjuAmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=6b5b121e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201107%2F3RSPWCT6QRCKRFXAXTBSIPA3AI%2F&h=c8cbe7b7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201107/3RSPWCT6QRCKRFXAXTBSIPA3AI/</a>"},{"pid":"8ca35bb0b82302199f9d165113e728166410105f","tid":2275202,"uid":38539,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T03:47:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/69DcnDc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F69DcnDc.png&h=13bce925&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o8dWPiL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo8dWPiL.png&h=e227409e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8668912c1d5cc9479de696ec8278223a135c0add","tid":2275202,"uid":165368,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T03:47:57.000Z","msg":"426再嘈我minecraft直播殺熊貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomo